zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613943\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jly1665702640894.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jly1665702640894.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jly1665702640894.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jly1665702640894\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Tab Height (TabHeight)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Height of all tabs in the widget, in character cells.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jly1665702640894__p_d107669e1_d107670e1_d107671e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TabHeight<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code> |\n         <var class=\"keyword varname\">DecimalNumber</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DecimalNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__2\"> Height in character cells; can be expressed as a\n                     decimal fraction, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">.7</code> or\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">2.5</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> (default) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12686e1_d12687e1_d12688e1__entry__2\">\n Height of each tab is based on the height of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Default Image</span>, if defined, or the height of the label. If the total widget height is smaller than the tab height, the widget height is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jly1665702640894__section_h3b_v1z_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1046835e122\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jly1665702640894__table_d12689e1_d12690e1_d12691e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jly1665702640894__section_ogk_1bz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1046835e168\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jly1665702640894__p_d107678e1_d107679e1_d107680e1\">Use this property only if the tab height does fit\n            the selected font and you want the height to be smaller or larger than the cell\n            height.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jly1665702640894__section_vzq_bbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1046835e177\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jly1665702640894__p_d107684e1_d107685e1_d107686e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jly1665702640894__pre_n5w_cbz_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabHeight=1.5\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jly1665702640894__section_ofb_dbz_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1046835e210\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613943\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613943\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Height (TabHeight) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Tab Height (TabHeight) Height of all tabs in the widget, in character cells. \" TabHeight = 0 | DecimalNumber \" Value Description DecimalNumber Height in character cells; can be expressed as a decimal fraction, for example .7 or 2.5 . 0 (default) Height of each tab is based on the height of the Default Image , if defined, or the height of the label. If the total widget height is smaller than the tab height, the widget height is used. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Use this property only if the tab height does fit the selected font and you want the height to be smaller or larger than the cell height. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabHeight=1.5\" Copy Applies To utabex (TabEx) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}